{"tid":1181531,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"(懷舊系列) 講到電音，我始終都係鍾意 90年代到2000初嘅作品","createTime":"2019-06-01T16:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T01:43:29.000Z","uid":106212,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ed41972b3e4d572c1964c6b57c0d0a98467a737f","tid":1181531,"uid":106212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"雖然今時今日有好多電音嘅歌曲，但我始終都係鍾意 90年代到2000年代初嘅作品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多都好經典，我拋磚幾首先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Butterfly - Smile dk</strong><br />\n以前 dance dance revolution 跳舞機開始帶起嘅呢首歌，我相信80後90後一定有聽過<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B_qwUS8Uqjg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DB_qwUS8Uqjg&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=cf7a1734\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B_qwUS8Uqjg</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Barbie Girl - Aqua</strong><br />\n印象中以前啲服裝店、髮廊都會播呢首歌，睇MTV頻道又係成日播，身邊同學又係度唱 life is plastic it's fantastic<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZyhrYis509A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZyhrYis509A&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=6f5844ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZyhrYis509A</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Dragostea Din Tei - O-Zone</strong><br />\nMa-ia-hii Ma-ia-hoo，呢首歌唔好話80後90後，分分鐘00後都有聽過，呢首真係 hit 到街知巷聞，個時仲有好多搞笑嘅同音歌詞改編作品<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YnopHCL1Jk8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYnopHCL1Jk8&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=ba2a0a85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YnopHCL1Jk8</a><br />\n<br />\n依家聽返都仲係咁正，唔會覺得 out&nbsp; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正評係畀經典電音作品嘅 &nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5e1cace7a2719797a8b46fee8a46d69994870e","tid":1181531,"uid":106212,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:36:21.000Z","msg":"Smile dk 同 Aqua 呢兩個組合仲有好多經典電音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Boys - Smile dk</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ObyDKXHHshM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DObyDKXHHshM&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=7ec13fb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ObyDKXHHshM</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>My Oh My - Aqua</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OG0AvwM_QAI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOG0AvwM_QAI&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=2ef469ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OG0AvwM_QAI</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Dr. Jones - Aqua</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-1jPUB7gRyg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-1jPUB7gRyg&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=e623e26b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-1jPUB7gRyg</a>"},{"pid":"dd811afb30ec488bb2bdbbb418827758875fbbda","tid":1181531,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:40:10.000Z","msg":"最中意GrooveJet，到依家都係"},{"pid":"b8cc5f82a8c55c443d9fea852aa0b0a458bbe551","tid":1181531,"uid":106212,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:45:31.000Z","msg":"介紹多幾首 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Crazy Frog - Axel F</strong><br />\n呢首近乎係無歌詞，純電音，好正，我諗好多人都聽過<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k85mRPqvMbE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dk85mRPqvMbE&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=30c7ded9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k85mRPqvMbE</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Dub I Dub - Me &amp; My</strong><br />\n呢苜都係跳舞機嘅熱門歌，但未必係好純正電音<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XTjJ2_P5P4U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXTjJ2_P5P4U&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=16100110\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XTjJ2_P5P4U</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Boom Boom Boom Boom - Vengaboys </strong><br />\n荷蘭組合Vengaboys嘅經典歌曲，呢首係當年歐洲舞曲風格 Eurodance 中非常出名<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xMP-JqFQ_l4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxMP-JqFQ_l4&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=e45e8226\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xMP-JqFQ_l4</a>"},{"pid":"30b0fbf24069c1a3a1e5b3082742b3aa129436e8","tid":1181531,"uid":106212,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:51:46.000Z","msg":"再介紹幾首<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Blue (Da Ba Dee) - Eiffel 65 </strong><br />\n呢首都係當年歐洲舞曲風格Eurodance 中嘅表表者，2000年代香港 Disco 都會播呢首歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zA52uNzx7Y4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzA52uNzx7Y4&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=3cbed1c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zA52uNzx7Y4</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我的驕傲 Proud of you  (Remix)</strong><br />\n容祖兒嘅我的驕傲 大家都聽過，但 Remix 版有無聽過？呢首 Remix 當年好hit，仲收錄係電音精選唱片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FFMbDmUBK5o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFFMbDmUBK5o&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=f6fca8e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FFMbDmUBK5o</a>"},{"pid":"ff575d40ba342def42ab6511eef1abed6100f84e","tid":1181531,"uid":193548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T1